==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Boswellian
<hw>Bos*well"i*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Relating to, or
characteristic of, <person>Dr. Johnson's</person> biographer,
<person>James <etsep>Boswell</etsep></person>, whose hero worship made
his narrative a faithful but often uncritical record of details.</def>
-- <wordforms><wf>Bos"well*ize</wf> <pr>(#)</pr>, <pos>v. i. &
t.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Boswellism</ent>⟦br⟧
